# Skips Counter — environment variables
#
# Prototype phase: no environment variables are required.
# The app submits skip events directly to each manager's Google Apps Script
# Web App URL (configured in src/config/managers.js), which handles all
# Sheets API writes server-side without client-side OAuth tokens.
#
# Environment variables will be added here when production Google Workspace
# OAuth is introduced for the service-account approach.
